Name:           ffnvcodec
Version:        11.0.10.0
Release:        0
Summary:        FFmpeg version of NVIDIA codec API headers
License:        MIT
Group:          Development/Libraries/C and C++
URL:            https://git.videolan.org/?p=ffmpeg/nv-codec-headers.git
Source:         nv-codec-headers-%{version}.tar.xz
